c0000115
00:05:37.210 --> 00:05:39.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't look away from me.
- Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!</b></Default>

c0000116
00:05:39.590 --> 00:05:41.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>During Kaede's symptoms,</b></Default>

c0000117
00:05:41.380 --> 00:05:44.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I met a reporter who
