c0000149
00:06:50.870 --> 00:06:53.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sometime soon I intend
to resume my on-camera work.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:55.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- But not under</b></Default>

c0000151
00:06:55.370 --> 00:06:56.920 line:90% align:center
