c0000158
00:07:11.260 --> 00:07:13.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I
just thought more about what
you said and you were right.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:07:13.980 --> 00:07:16.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really liked acting in dramas
