c0000160
00:07:16.270 --> 00:07:18.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I wanted to do them forever.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:07:19.360 --> 00:07:22.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe I started getting symptoms
