00:13:49.790 --> 00:13:53.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, I was in love.
It's in the past now.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:13:53.500 --> 00:13:55.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She's arrived.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000327
00:13:56.130 --> 00:13:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who is that?</b></Default>

c0000328
00:13:58.550 --> 00:14:00.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"To Manager?"</b></Default>

c0000329
00:14:00.090 --> 00:14:02.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait a minute!
That's your mother?</b></Default>

c0000330
00:14:02.130 --> 00:14:04.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I
need to discuss
my return with her.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:14:04.300 --> 00:14:06.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I figured she should know
I'm going to sign a contract</b></Default>

c0000332
00:14:06.760 --> 00:14:08.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a different agency.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:14:08.510 --> 00:14:10.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you sure you're
gonna be okay?</b></Default>

c0000334
00:14:10.560 --> 00:14:12.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- After I talk to her,
we can continue our date.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:14:13.060 --> 00:14:14.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So wait here.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:14:16.230 --> 00:14:17.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000337
00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:27.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasping]</b></Default>

c0000338
00:14:29.580 --> 00:14:30.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000339
00:14:30.910 --> 00:14:32.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're kidding me.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:14:33.160 --> 00:14:34.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Interesting.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:14:34.370 --> 00:14:36.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I take it you're
the one who called me out</b></Default>

c0000342
00:14:36.170 --> 00:14:37.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to this place?
Who are you?</b></Default>

c0000343
00:14:37.880 --> 00:14:39.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what do you want?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:14:42.090 --> 00:14:44.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- My name's Sakuta Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:14:44.720 --> 00:14:47.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I go to school with Mai.
- Um, with who?</b></Default>

c0000346
00:14:47.350 --> 00:14:48.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know, Mai.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:14:49.180 --> 00:14:50.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Should I know her?</b></Default>

c0000348
00:14:50.390 --> 00:14:51.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Seriously?</b></Default>

c0000349
00:14:52.310 --> 00:14:53.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't know
your own daughter?</b></Default>

c0000350
00:14:53.850 --> 00:14:55.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What in the world
are you talking about?</b></Default>

c0000351
00:14:55.730 --> 00:14:57.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't have a daughter.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:14:57.150 --> 00:14:58.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this a joke?</b></Default>

c0000353
00:14:58.520 --> 00:14:59.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I should be asking that!</b></Default>

c0000354
00:14:59.770 --> 00:15:01.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The text!</b></Default>

c0000355
00:15:01.610 --> 00:15:02.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The one about meeting
here today.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:15:03.070 --> 00:15:04.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You mean this?</b></Default>

c0000357
00:15:04.450 --> 00:15:06.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't figure out who
the sender is.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:15:06.910 --> 00:15:09.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- I remember forcing myself</b></Default>

c0000359
00:15:09.450 --> 00:15:11.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to make time to fit
this appointment in.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:15:12.200 --> 00:15:13.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why did I do that, though?</b></Default>

c0000361
00:15:13.910 --> 00:15:15.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, this doesn't make
any sense.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:15:15.920 --> 00:15:17.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aren't you her mother?</b></Default>

c0000363
00:15:17.290 --> 00:15:18.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How can you forget about
your own daughter?</b></Default>

c0000364
00:15:18.880 --> 00:15:20.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's enough!</b></Default>

c0000365
00:15:20.170 --> 00:15:22.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But why?
We haven't finished talking yet!</b></Default>

c0000366
00:15:22.380 --> 00:15:23.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please, stop it.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:15:23.710 --> 00:15:25.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Go pull pranks
on somebody else.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:15:25.720 --> 00:15:27.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've wasted enough
of my time.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:15:31.560 --> 00:15:32.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [crying]</b></Default>

c0000370
00:15:33.680 --> 00:15:35.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, excuse me.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:15:35.560 --> 00:15:37.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you heard
of Mai Sakurajima?</b></Default>

c0000372
00:15:37.810 --> 00:15:39.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was on that hit
morning drama.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:15:39.730 --> 00:15:41.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm, don't know her.
Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:15:41.940 --> 00:15:43.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000375
00:15:44.570 --> 00:15:48.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The results of being invisible
isn't just the loss</b></Default>

c0000376
00:15:48.200 --> 00:15:50.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of being seen,</b></Default>

c0000377
00:15:50.200 --> 00:15:53.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but also the loss
of people's memory of her?</b></Default>

c0000378
00:15:53.240 --> 00:15:56.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mai Sakurajima?
Who's that?</b></Default>

c0000379
00:15:56.120 --> 00:15:57.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000380
00:15:57.370 --> 00:15:58.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hello?</b></Default>

c0000381
00:15:58.790 --> 00:16:00.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You really aren't familiar
with that name?</b></Default>

c0000382
00:16:01.420 --> 00:16:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nope. Should I be?</b></Default>

c0000383
00:16:03.090 --> 00:16:04.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What about my photo?</b></Default>

c0000384
00:16:04.710 --> 00:16:07.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I already promised
I wouldn't disclose it.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:16:07.130 --> 00:16:10.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you remember?
- Who did you promise that to?</b></Default>

c0000386
00:16:10.090 --> 00:16:12.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It was you.
How do you not remember that?</b></Default>

c0000387
00:16:14.930 --> 00:16:16.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thanks for today.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:16:16.230 --> 00:16:17.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Later.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:16:18.100 --> 00:16:19.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, wait!</b></Default>

c0000390
00:16:19.520 --> 00:16:21.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai, please, let's go!</b></Default>

c0000391
00:16:21.770 --> 00:16:23.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What? Go where?</b></Default>

c0000392
00:16:23.360 --> 00:16:25.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- To a city somewhere far away!</b></Default>

c0000393
00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:27.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe we'll find people there
who can still see you!</b></Default>

c0000394
00:16:28.280 --> 00:16:29.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's find out.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:16:29.320 --> 00:16:30.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [shudders]</b></Default>

c0000396
00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:31.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What happens when we do?</b></Default>

c0000397
00:16:32.530 --> 00:16:34.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the point of knowing
that no one except you</b></Default>

c0000398
00:16:34.540 --> 00:16:36.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is able to see or remember me?</b></Default>

c0000399
00:16:37.040 --> 00:16:39.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- At least while
you're figuring it out.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:16:39.170 --> 00:16:40.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be by your side
the whole time.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:16:43.500 --> 00:16:45.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Bold, for someone younger
than me.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:16:45.760 --> 00:16:47.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It is a date, after all.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:16:49.090 --> 00:16:50.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- All right, fine.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:16:50.840 --> 00:16:53.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're saying you don't want
to send me back home yet...</b></Default>

c0000405
00:16:53.720 --> 00:16:55.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can continue our date, then.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:16:57.600 --> 00:16:59.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please leave a message after
the tone.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:16:59.890 --> 00:17:01.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[beeps]</b></Default>

c0000408
00:17:01.270 --> 00:17:02.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede, it's me.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:17:04.730 --> 00:17:07.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother?
You're calling so late.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:17:07.190 --> 00:17:09.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry, I won't
be home tonight.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:17:09.700 --> 00:17:10.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's an errand
I've gotta run.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:17:11.570 --> 00:17:14.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Really?
What kind of errand?</b></Default>

c0000413
00:17:14.160 --> 00:17:16.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Do you remember a girl named
Mai Sakurajima who came by</b></Default>

c0000414
00:17:17.080 --> 00:17:19.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a while back?
- No. I don't think so.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:17:20.040 --> 00:17:21.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't worry, then.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:17:21.620 --> 00:17:23.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's instant noodles in
the kitchen cabinet.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:17:23.670 --> 00:17:24.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can have that for dinner.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:17:26.000 --> 00:17:27.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll call you later.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:17:30.130 --> 00:17:32.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In the Gifu prefecture
its population is second</b></Default>

c0000420
00:17:32.970 --> 00:17:34.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to Gifu itself.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:17:34.390 --> 00:17:35.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What city is that?</b></Default>

c0000422
00:17:35.600 --> 00:17:37.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ogaki.
It's where we're headed to.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:17:37.930 --> 00:17:39.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:17:39.390 --> 00:17:41.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- They also have tons
of underground water.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:17:41.730 --> 00:17:44.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Any place with clean water's
good in my book.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:17:45.560 --> 00:17:48.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, Sakuta.
- Do you need something?</b></Default>

c0000427
00:17:48.570 --> 00:17:51.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you able to see me?</b></Default>

c0000428
00:17:51.150 --> 00:17:54.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yep, like always.
- Can you hear me?</b></Default>

c0000429
00:17:54.160 --> 00:17:55.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, perfectly.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:17:55.530 --> 00:17:57.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And do you remember me?</b></Default>

c0000431
00:17:57.790 --> 00:17:59.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mai Sakurajima.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:18:00.000 --> 00:18:02.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a third-year student
at Minegahara High School.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You made your TV debut
at six years old</b></Default>

c0000434
00:18:05.590 --> 00:18:07.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and have had many roles sense.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:18:07.460 --> 00:18:09.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Personality-wise,
you're twisted and vague.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:18:09.960 --> 00:18:11.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Excuse me?</b></Default>

c0000437
00:18:11.590 --> 00:18:14.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're so uncertain but you
try your best to hide it.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:18:16.050 --> 00:18:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't remember saying you
could hold my hand.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:18:18.970 --> 00:18:20.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But I wanted to.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:18:23.520 --> 00:18:24.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- All right, fine.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:18:24.940 --> 00:18:26.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only for a little bit, though.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:18:30.110 --> 00:18:32.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, do you know
who Mai Sakurajima is?</b></Default>

c0000443
00:18:33.150 --> 00:18:35.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You may have seen her in
a bullet train commercial.</b></Default>

c0000444
00:18:35.320 --> 00:18:36.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakurajima?</b></Default>

c0000445
00:18:36.990 --> 00:18:38.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're saying there
was an actress by that name?</b></Default>

c0000446
00:18:38.740 --> 00:18:40.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
Never mind.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:18:43.330 --> 00:18:44.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So cramped.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:18:44.670 --> 00:18:46.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not surprising.</b></Default>

c0000449
00:18:46.500 --> 00:18:47.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bath time.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:18:48.170 --> 00:18:49.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000451
00:18:50.420 --> 00:18:51.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You better not peek.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:18:51.760 --> 00:18:53.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No need to fret.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:18:53.260 --> 00:18:55.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could easily fill up
three times just</b></Default>

c0000454
00:18:55.130 --> 00:18:56.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from hearing the shower.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:18:56.470 --> 00:18:57.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000456
00:18:58.300 --> 00:18:59.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000457
00:18:59.850 --> 00:19:02.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Making a guy writhe
in agony by using sound</b></Default>

c0000458
00:19:02.310 --> 00:19:03.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to fuel his imagination.</b></Default>

c0000459
00:19:03.850 --> 00:19:05.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Typical behavior
of a mature woman,</b></Default>

c0000460
00:19:05.600 --> 00:19:07.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which you definitely are.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:19:07.770 --> 00:19:09.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You don't need
to tell me that!</b></Default>

c0000462
00:19:09.150 --> 00:19:11.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not dumb!
But seriously,</b></Default>

c0000463
00:19:11.190 --> 00:19:13.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>don't start doing
weird stuff out here!</b></Default>

c0000464
00:19:13.240 --> 00:19:14.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Weird? Like what?</b></Default>

c0000465
00:19:15.320 --> 00:19:16.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You dummy!</b></Default>

c0000466
00:19:16.610 --> 00:19:17.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do whatever!</b></Default>

c0000467
00:19:19.240 --> 00:19:21.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Adorable.
Cutest thing she's done yet.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:19:24.580 --> 00:19:25.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone trilling]</b></Default>

c0000469
00:19:25.710 --> 00:19:26.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[receiver clicks]
- Hello?</b></Default>

c0000470
00:19:26.830 --> 00:19:28.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, hello?</b></Default>

c0000471
00:19:28.170 --> 00:19:29.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Kunimi.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:19:29.710 --> 00:19:31.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Do you even know what time
it is?</b></Default>

c0000473
00:19:31.750 --> 00:19:33.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's 1:16 a.m.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:19:33.710 --> 00:19:36.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Exactly,
so why are you calling?</b></Default>

c0000475
00:19:36.130 --> 00:19:38.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's an emergency.
I need to ask for your help.</b></Default>

c0000476
00:19:38.590 --> 00:19:40.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sure. What's up?</b></Default>

c0000477
00:19:40.680 --> 00:19:42.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> - Do you remember Mai Sakurajia
at all?</b></Default>

c0000478
00:19:42.850 --> 00:19:44.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? Of course I do.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:19:44.930 --> 00:19:47.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You don't, right?
I should have--</b></Default>

c0000480
00:19:47.100 --> 00:19:49.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wait, you remember?
Are you sure about that?</b></Default>

c0000481
00:19:49.900 --> 00:19:52.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, I'm sure.
You feeling okay?</b></Default>

c0000482
00:19:52.780 --> 00:19:53.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that it?</b></Default>

c0000483
00:19:53.780 --> 00:19:54.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going back to sleep.</b></Default>

c0000484
00:19:54.860 --> 00:19:56.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hold on!</b></Default>

c0000485
00:19:56.280 --> 00:19:58.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you mind giving me
Futaba's phone number?</b></Default>

c0000486
00:19:58.950 --> 00:20:01.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Do you even know what time
it is right now?</b></Default>

c0000487
00:20:01.370 --> 00:20:03.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's 1:19 in the morning.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:20:03.200 --> 00:20:05.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's 21 past.
Your clock's a bit slow.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:20:05.750 --> 00:20:06.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000490
00:20:07.960 --> 00:20:09.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:20:09.580 --> 00:20:11.880 line:90% align:center
